sequenceDiagram
    participant USER as Userspace (FFmpeg)
    participant V4L2 as V4L2 Core
    participant CEDRUS as Cedrus Driver
    participant VPU as VPU Hardware
    USER->>USER: Parse H.264 bitstream
    USER->>V4L2: Set controls (SPS, PPS, Slice)
    USER->>V4L2: QBUF OUTPUT (bitstream)
    USER->>V4L2: QBUF CAPTURE (frame buffer)
    USER->>V4L2: STREAMON
    V4L2->>CEDRUS: device_run()
    CEDRUS->>VPU: Program registers
    CEDRUS->>VPU: Start decode
    VPU-->>CEDRUS: IRQ (complete)
    CEDRUS-->>V4L2: job_finish()
    V4L2-->>USER: DQBUF (decoded frame)
